<title>USA: IPO FILING - ECsoft Group plc.</title>
<headline>IPO FILING - ECsoft Group plc.</headline>
<dateline>WASHINGTON 1996-11-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Company Name		   ECsoft Group plc</p>
<p>Stock symbol			 ECSGY.O</p>
<p>Estimated price range per ADS $10-12/shr</p>
<p>Total American Depositary</p>
<p>    shares to be offered	 3.0 million, representing 3.0</p>
<p>					  million ordinary shares</p>
<p>Shrs offered by company	 2.1 million</p>
<p>Shrs offered by shareholders  900,000 Ordinary shrs outstanding</p>
<p>    after ipo			7,118,611</p>
<p>Lead Underwriter    Robertson, Stephens &amp; Co</p>
<p>Underwriters over-allotment  450,000 ADSs  </p>
<p>Business: The company provides information technology consulting, applications development and systems integration to large European-based companies. The company is based in Berkhamsted, Hertfordshire, England. Use of Proceeds: To repay debt incurred in connection with the acquisition of ECsoft Nordic AS, ECsoft Holdings P.L.C. and ECsoft S.A. and for general corporate purposes and working capital purposes.</p>
